    <div class="hero-sub">We Watch the Eruv So You Don't Have To</div>
    <p class="hero-tagline">An automated, real-time eruv monitoring system — affordable, solar-powered, and built for communities of every size. No more weekly perimeter walks. No more missed breaks.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
